    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "Medecins Du Monde (MdM-F) will be responsible for project development and effective implementation, together with local implementing partner Bheri Environmental Excellence Group (BEE Group) in close coordination with Nepalgunj Sub-Metropolitan City and Khajura RM, Duduwa RM in Banke district. MdM-F headquarters is seeking the donor for this project, and will transfer the required budget to partners on an instalment basis, in advance. All the partners will have their own administration, procurement and finance policies which meet the requirements of all organizations and work within the applicable laws of Nepal."
      },
